main event: A UFO sighting was reported in the Lake Charles area on 13 AUG 61, which was later identified as a M-31 para-flare.
interesting points: The sighting occurred at approximately 2030 local time on 13 AUG 61., The object was recovered on 14 AUG 61 at 1500 local time., The sighting was significant enough to be reported in the local newspaper., The Air Force categorized the event as not a target of interest., The conclusions suggested the object was probably a balloon or possibly a balloon.
